                         ወማቴዎስ፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ ወተፈዊሰነ፡ ከመ፡ <cb n="b"/><supplied reason="lost" resp="DN"/>
                         ተንሥኣ፡ ሊቅ፡ ወደቅነ፡ በገጽነ፨
                         </incipit>
                         <note>Divided into 59 sections. The part <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2444Temher"/> is
                         located on <locus from="33ra" to="38ra"/>.</note>
                        </msItem>


